鸟是其中的一部分，被单独抽出来了 ...</div><br />\n看点是秀一基被丽奈一路吊打么<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/016.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"334","username":"Bani82","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"334","dbdateline":"1543947401","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41830708","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"starrin","authorid":"169050","dateline":"2018-12-5 02:21","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830700&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Bani82 发表于 2018-12-5 02:16</font></a><br />\n看点是秀一基被丽奈一路吊打么</div><br />\n久美子和秀一一起逛了县祭哦，那段还很甜的。<br />\n逛完后久美子就去找丽奈了。<br />\n“冢本呢？”<br />\n“我让他先回去了”<br />\n“你怎么能这样对人家”","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"335","username":"starrin","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"335","dbdateline":"1543947706","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41830716","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"堆雪若叶","authorid":"454538","dateline":"2018-12-5 02:24","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830584&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">osore 发表于 2018-12-5 01:50</font></a><br />\r\n和TV第二季有很多地方有呼应<br />\r\n简单说一下印象深的几点：<br />\r\n一是退部那次希美对小肥宅的处理，可以看出和这次的 ...</div><br />\n第二季里和好和剧场版和好内涵还是相差蛮大的，包括重复“喜欢霙的双簧管”这句的区别。二季里实际上把霙拉出来的是优子，希美只是最后搭上手，“喜欢霙的双簧管”只是给霙坚定吹下去的理由；而这里“喜欢霙的双簧管”是纯粹的自白，并非出于霙的期待而是自己的坦诚。所以二季的和好当时看下来是略显虚浮的，希美并没有对霙的心意做出回应，而到这里才是真实的答复，那么收尾还是很安心的。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"336","username":"堆雪若叶","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"336","dbdateline":"1543947886","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41830725","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"astrayveller","authorid":"505868","dateline":"2018-12-5 02:26","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1