妒霙，或者说羡慕，羡慕霙的才华<br />\r\n这个不太好表达<br />\r\n也不是什么不好的感 ...</div><br />\n太不像话了<br />\r\n得出这种结论，连我自己都感觉震惊","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"346","username":"中川夏纪","adminid":"0","groupid":"30","memberstatus":"0","number":"346","dbdateline":"1543949790","groupiconid":"6"},{"pid":"41830816","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"炯Ⅺ","authorid":"232211","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:11","message":"看完熟肉，真的好看，文艺百合片，音乐很好听，第三乐章那段用音乐表达感情的独奏相当牛逼，太神了。<br />\r\n其实很简单的一个故事，但山田尚子真的牛逼，用文艺的拍摄手法和出色的镜头语言，细细表达着纤细复杂而又有点沉重的感情，一个半小时的时间里完全不会感到沉闷。<br />\r\n肚子里墨水有限，真是不知道如何用语言形容，总之就是好看，今年看过的最好看的动画剧场版。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"347","username":"炯Ⅺ","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"347","dbdateline":"1543950660","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41830829","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"坂木静香","authorid":"427168","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:17","message":"这脖子。。。。为什么京阿尼作画还要特地表现脖子？","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"348","username":"坂木静香","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"348","dbdateline":"1543951077","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830830","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"wuaistage1","authorid":"471200","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:18","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830790&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-5 02:54</font></a><br />\r\n有一个问题，是不是其实希美还是有些嫉妒霙，或者说羡慕，羡慕霙的才华<br />\r\n这个不太好表达<br />\r\n也不是什么不好的感 ...</div><br />\n有啊，原本就是还有嫉妒的成分在，剧场淡化了这一点，后面的转变释然才显得顺畅起来。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至于结局就是TE啦，之前看那么多访谈，总结起来大致就一个意思：<font color=\"#ff0000\">两人其实一直没真正对等过，但到剧场结束时终于有走向对等的趋势了。相互放开对方才是真正迈向对方的第一步。</font><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n总之，未来是美好的。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"349","username":"wuaistage1","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"349","dbdateline":"1543951101","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41830834","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"堆雪若叶","authorid":"454538","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:18","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830790&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-5 02:54</font></a><br />\r\n有一个问题，是不是其实希美还是有些嫉妒霙，或者说羡慕，羡慕霙的才华<br />\r\n这个不太好表达<br />\r\n也不是什么不好的感 ...</div><br />\n希美去在意霙的才华很正常吧，尤其是她还没能意识到自己对霙异样的感情时，在意更突显了对比的落差心理，衍生出各种情绪都是自然的。但是这并不是构成希美感情的全部，最后希美回忆起和霙的初见应该才是促成她追赶霙的原因，那是吹奏之前的初心。所以无论这之后有多少不对等和差异，起初两个人就是相合在一块的啊。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"350","username":"堆雪若叶","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"350","dbdateline":"1543951122","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41830839","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"枫凛劫火","authorid":"217784","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:20","message":"我词穷了 后面随着矛盾开始几乎是全程窒息 情感随着画面喷薄而出 每一个镜头都才华横溢 这帮人太厉害了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"351","username":"枫凛劫火","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"351","dbdateline":"1543951228","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41830848","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:23","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830655&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">Bani82 发表于 2018-12-5 02:02</font></a><br />\r\n下一部是说什么？下一部部长都是黄高了吧，青鸟这队不是走了么？<br />\r\n秀一还有机会演爱情故事？原作都被甩了， ...</div><br />\n下一部，二年级的久美子，时间上应该是并行的，主要是久美子和低音部的新人。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"352","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"352","dbdateline":"1543951415","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41830872","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"天天座理世","authorid":"385180","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:32","message":"伞木希美出来挨打","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"353","username":"天天座理世","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"353","dbdateline":"1543951973","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830889","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-12-5 03:44","message":"当日出熟肉还是很出人意料，这速度，梦回字幕组黄金时代。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"354","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"354","dbdateline":"1543952652","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41830909","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-5 04:02","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830834&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">堆雪若叶 发表于 2018-12-5 03:18</font></a><br />\r\n希美去在意霙的才华很正常吧，尤其是她还没能意识到自己对霙异样的感情时，在意更突显了对比的落差心理， ...</div><br />\n哈哈，我知道羡慕啊嫉妒什么的并不是希美感情的全部，所以说她们感情复杂啊<br />\r\n@wuaistage1<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且两只鸟不是在一起了吗，希美回忆之后 特意给了大约28秒的镜头<br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201812/05/035625qeos5gqzos4qtpjz.jpg\" attach=\"41830909\" /></div><br />\r\n那么问题来了这是什么鸟，这又是什么花<br />\r\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201812/05/035940tg2ue7bq4gemz4mg.jpg\" attach=\"41830909\" /></div><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n最后的英文dis joint，dis被划掉变成joint，也能说明监督的想法了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"355","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"355","dbdateline":"1543953740","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830955","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"无名之歌","authorid":"474048","dateline":"2018-12-5 04:34","message":"得了半年多臆病，我给的都是金像奖的期望。看下来感觉反而没有那么强<br />\n不过still okay，伞哥哥扭曲的小人格，爱死了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/062.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\nps：可能也是因为半年时间已经用各种pv把这片子参透了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/002.png\" /><br />\n— from samsung SM-N950F, Android 8.0.0 of <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mi43uRm\">S1 Next Goose</a> v2.0.2","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"356","username":"无名之歌","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"356","dbdateline":"1543955642","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830961","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"无名之歌","authorid":"474048","dateline":"2018-12-5 04:36","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830404&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2018-12-5 03:11</font></a><br />\n所以问个问题，为什么梨々花第一次自称的时候把姓氏叫成“鎧…“，马上改口剑崎，而且后面新山老师同样喊成 ...</div><br />\n字比较容易联想到吧，还有rrk叫错可能是因为太在意霙了<br />\n<br />\n— from samsung SM-N950F, Android 8.0.0 of <a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1mi43uRm\">S1 Next Goose</a> v2.0.2","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"357","username":"无名之歌","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"357","dbdateline":"1543955803","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830970","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2018-12-5 04:43","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830790&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-4 18:54</font></a><br />\r\n有一个问题，是不是其实希美还是有些嫉妒霙，或者说羡慕，羡慕霙的才华<br />\r\n这个不太好表达<br />\r\n也不是什么不好的感 ...</div><br />\n直白地说，是有的。原作里表现地比吉田的剧情更明显。原作里希美的负面情绪带有强烈的”嫉妒“情感，因为她已经愈发明白霙在音乐上的天份是自己无法比拟的。而吉田和山田将这份嫉妒淡化了，演变成了以”自卑“为主导的心理，或者说就是你提到的”羡慕“。<br />\r\n我个人觉得这个情感的棘手之处在于，希美和霙的感情依托是靠乐器维系的，这一点与久丽差别很大。久丽的感情基础并不因音乐而维系，而是因为两人本身具有极其相似的内核，她们的精神世界是互通的，是相互理解的，而希美和霙恰恰不是，这也是本作试图体现的主题。所以”嫉妒“这个点在处理的时候，就会变成刺，变成尖锐的，可以几乎将二者感情纽带的东西斩断的”危险品“。看山田和吉田的访谈，就能发现她俩着重表现的是从”恋“到”爱“的转变过程，而嫉妒这个情绪太过强烈，就与整体基调并不吻合，所以吉田就动手魔改了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"358","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"358","dbdateline":"1543956194","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41830976","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-5 04:47","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830839&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">枫凛劫火 发表于 2018-12-5 03:20</font></a><br />\r\n我词穷了 后面随着矛盾开始几乎是全程窒息 情感随着画面喷薄而出 每一个镜头都才华横溢 这帮人太厉害了 ...</div><br />\n嗯嗯嗯，每一个镜头，表情，眼神，动作<br />\r\n这所有的细节，真的是太厉害了<br />\r\n细节决定成败，这片就是细节的全面胜利<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想截一大堆动图啊，然而图太大传不上来<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等等，我好像又想到一件事，明天再说<br />\r\n果然这片应该多看几遍啊<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"359","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"359","dbdateline":"1543956447","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41831001","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2018-12-5 05:03","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41830961&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">无名之歌 发表于 2018-12-4 20:36</font></a><br />\r\n字比较容易联想到吧，还有rrk叫错可能是因为太在意霙了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n— from samsung SM-N950F, Android 8.0.0 of S1 ...</div><br />\n所以就是”剑盾“说么...这个点我第一次看得时候就觉得很有意思，按理说如果梨梨花一个人说错可以被认为是在意霙，新山老师也说错总觉得很奇怪，这个角色无论tv还是剧场里，都是一副很知性，很有见解的老师形象出现的，难得口误一次，感觉背后肯定有什么设计意图","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"360","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"360","dbdateline":"1543957429","groupiconid":"8"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":{"41830786":[]},"commentcount":{"41830786":null},"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"th